                  "working": "$4312 \\div 2 = 2156$\n$2156 \\div 2 = 1078$\n$1078 \\div 2 = 539$\n$539$ is not divisible by 3 or 5. Try 7: $539 \\div 7 = 77$\n$77 \\div 7 = 11$\n$11$ is prime.",
